# ⚠️ 7. WHERE PEOPLE USUALLY FAIL (IMPORTANT)

If you don’t define this clearly, you will get bugs like:

### ❌ invalid transitions:

* skipping steps
* double approvals
* re-activating roles
* inconsistent flow states

---

# 🔥 8. FINAL “RULE SET” SUMMARY

## ONBOARDING FLOW

```text
IN_PROGRESS → COMPLETED | FAILED
```

## STEP DATA

```text
NOT_STARTED → IN_PROGRESS → SUBMITTED → APPROVED | REJECTED
```

## APPROVALS

```text
PENDING → APPROVED | REJECTED
```

## ROLE ACTIVATION RULE

```text
IF flow COMPLETED AND no approval needed → activate role
IF approval APPROVED → activate role
```

